# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/

# Session clock (ephemeral per-run start timestamp written by tools/session-clock.sh;
# lives only inside the run container, reported into the journal, never committed)
.session-clock

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# Secrets / local config
.env
*.env

# Local-only experiment artifacts (raw model outputs that are huge or contain
# wholesale third-party text). Curated outputs belong in experiments/runs/ and
# are committed; raw scratch goes here.
experiments/data/scratch/
experiments/data/raw/

# Lancaster norms raw CSV (CC BY-4.0, re-downloadable; sha256 pinned in run record)
experiments/data/lancaster/
experiments/runs/2026-05-31-multimodal-grounding-image-v1/data/

# WiC dataset (CC BY-NC 4.0; re-downloadable, sha256 pinned in run record) + the
# gitignored local full-text the lexical-v3 probe reads. Commit only the recipe +
# manifest (ids/gold/stratum), never the corpus example sentences.
experiments/data/wic/
experiments/runs/2026-05-31-lexical-polysemy-homonymy-v3/fulltext.jsonl

# Hawkins/Stanford tangrams repeated-reference corpus (GitHub license: null;
# authors' "open corpus" release statement only; re-downloadable, sha256 pinned in
# the resource page). Recipe-not-corpus posture: commit only the download recipe +
# the derived aggregate entrainment table, NEVER the raw utterances.
experiments/data/hawkins-tangrams/

# Mahowald 2023 aann-public mirror (MIT; re-clonable, upstream commit pinned in run record)
experiments/data/aann-public/

# languageR package tarball + extracted dative.rda (GPL-2|GPL-3; re-downloadable from
# CRAN, tarball sha256 pinned in the run record). Recipe-not-corpus posture: commit only
# the download/inspect recipe + the derived factor->probability table, NEVER the raw rows.
experiments/data/languageR/

# Scivetti et al. 2025 CxNLI repo (github.com/melissatorgbi/beyond-memorization; NO
# license file observed — recipe-not-corpus posture: commit only prep.py (the fetch +
# parse recipe), the sha-pinned manifest (counts + hash, NO premise/hypothesis text),
# and derived per-construction accuracies. NEVER the raw NLI item text. Re-clonable;
# upstream commit pinned in the run record + resource page.)
experiments/data/scivetti/

# Working-surface CoT for the let-alone format probe: the model's step-by-step
# reasoning RESTATES the unlicensed Scivetti premise/hypothesis text, so the full CoT
# is gitignored (recipe-not-corpus). Committed artifact is raw/{slot}-labels.json
# (item_id + gold + parsed label + content sha256 + usage, NO text); the CoT under
# raw/cot/ is for in-session parse/genuineness verification only and is re-derivable.
experiments/runs/2026-06-20-scivetti-let-alone-working-surface/raw/cot/
experiments/runs/2026-06-20-scivetti-let-alone-forced-decomposition/raw/cot/
experiments/runs/2026-06-20-scivetti-let-alone-powered-rerun/raw/cot/
experiments/runs/2026-06-21-scivetti-let-alone-repeated-runs/raw/cot/

# s178 TEMP: mute rep2 raw/ while the probe writes (removed before final commit)
experiments/runs/2026-07-04-aann-behavioral-gradient-rep2/raw/
